{
  "message": "feat(rch): add remote compilation probes for fcp-mesh-harness and fcp-registry\n\nAdd two new RCH (Remote Compilation Helper) probe projects that enable\nremote build verification for the mesh harness and registry crates:\n\n- .rch/probes/fcp-mesh-harness/ \u2014 Probe for the mesh test harness crate,\n  following the same structure as the existing fcp-core and fcp-host probes\n  (Cargo.toml, .cargo/config.toml, .rchignore, rust-toolchain.toml, src/main.rs)\n\n- .rch/probes/fcp-registry/ \u2014 Probe for the new registry crate\n  (Cargo.toml, .rchignore, rust-toolchain.toml)\n\nThese probes allow rch to verify that the mesh-harness and registry crates\ncompile cleanly on remote build workers, extending the existing probe\ncoverage that already covers fcp-core and fcp-host.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
